{
  "stem": "25178.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And the people we knew, they-- they shied away-- didn't want to be too close to us because, you know, you shouldn't be socializing with a Jew.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the man who ran the place, he, lived in Westmalle as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, his name was Gustaaf De Cock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he told me it would be better for me not to be in the same place with my brother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he decided to keep me in his home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took me to his home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had nine children of his own, lived in a big, big house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first thing he told me when we came into the house when I stayed there, he said there was one condition that he would take care of me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that condition was that I should be converted to Catholicism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So he educated me in Catholicism himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And of course, everything that was based on Catholicism, in his point of view, was the fact that the Jews were being punished for the crucifixion of Jesus.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said to me, for me, the perfect thing was to be a devout Catholic, and pray, and maybe I can get the sins away from, from my parents which they had inherited because of the crucifixion.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they could be returned safe after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, I was a little 12-year-old boy, who has never been exposed to any kind of religion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I put my whole heart in studying the Catholic religion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was baptized in-- on Easter day, 1943.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a devout Catholic, and I prayed real, real, real hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I prayed with such conviction that sometimes I was crying during my prayers.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
